05847d5b7b5238a9f8770245d1ce04ec0dff2790.query:
SELECT
    A.public_id AS public_id,
    A.username AS username
FROM account AS A
INNER JOIN account_session AS "AS" ON A.id = "AS".account_id
WHERE "AS".public_id = $1
  AND "AS".deleted IS NULL;

132d925ab7e126679d3dcb19b22bf856cce539b9.query:
INSERT INTO account_password(public_id, created, account_id, password_hash)
VALUES ($1,
        $2,
        (SELECT id FROM account WHERE account.public_id = $3),
        $4)

697d5718990490bcb08b0b8a016021ddf4c5a361.query:
UPDATE account_session
SET deleted = $2
WHERE public_id = $1
  AND deleted IS NULL;

6a6951324cf16454f1d0f62c575a55f3724d5671.query:
INSERT INTO account (public_id, created, username)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
RETURNING id;

DELETE
FROM account

RETURNING id;

8760ee3bfdd2a96f2f37b9198e69b733464f2ccb.query:
INSERT INTO account_session (public_id, created, account_id)

a4ca6232604f3cd629954a6685cd0831388f6c7a.query:
SELECT
    A.id AS id,
    AP.password_hash AS password_hash
FROM account AS A
INNER JOIN account_password AS AP ON A.id = AP.account_id
WHERE A.username = $1
  AND AP.deleted IS NULL

aa321a6f203014b44d76b21074d961e9d7ebcc94.query:
SELECT
    AP.public_id AS public_id,
    AP.password_hash AS password_hash
FROM account AS A
INNER JOIN account_password AS AP ON A.id = AP.account_id
WHERE A.public_id = $1
  AND AP.deleted IS NULL;
